		{
			dependencies: ["33B6F60F71DA7F4D"]
			description: [
				"Drill lubricant is colloquially called \"mud\", and a &2mudpit&r is just a literal pit where drilling mud is prepared."
				""
				"This &2mudpit&r is maybe &oslightly&r more sophisticated."
				""
				"&2Planetary core drill&r lubricants must be produced on site, so creating &6diesel-oil mud&r requires you to be on the &7Moon&r and creating &aOlefin Mud&r requires you to be on either &cMars&r or &eVenus&r."
			]
