		{
			dependencies: ["18E1960D8F093DBC"]
			description: [
				"Unlike the &2lunar surface drill&r, the &2planetary core drill&r can be fully automated and produce lunar resources endlessly. "
				""
				"To do this, you will need to establish a the &2PCD&r and a &2mudpit&r on the lunar surface, and supply the drill with &bdiesel-oil mud&r as lubricant. "
				""
				"This will yield &6ores&r and &7regolith&r, and has a chance of returning the lubricant in a &chot&r form that can be cooled with a &2vacuum freezer&r."
				""
				"The Moon is the a good source of &dtitanium&r, &eplatinum&r, and &alanthanides&r, but drilling the core is your only source of &7bedrock dust&r."
			]
			id: "5B27C24236868566"
